    "description": "Meow Legion 是一个关于组建一支猫咪军队来抵抗敌人波浪的游戏。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<strong>我我喜欢猫。</strong><li><strong>推荐使用手柄。</strong><br></li><li>左键/RT来<strong>射击</strong>。<br></li><li>右键/LT来<strong>召回</strong>猫咪。<br></li><li>召回让你的猫咪朝你移动并<strong>拾取物品</strong>。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/642c2ffcd1de6f27dafc696023268c18.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>共有10种类型的猫咪<br></li><li>每次失败后你会变得更强。你将收到一张随机的<strong>喵卡</strong>，每张都有不同的属性加成。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.webm?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/643c11d915b15170ec1c0d2270953469.mp4?t=1711995359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>请不要忘记携带<strong>喵卡</strong>。在下面显示的界面中，你可以选择你希望携带进战斗的喵卡。每只猫每场战斗只能携带一张喵卡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345550/extras/d025c878fb3ff619d8d17127bf64c819.poster.avif?t=1711995359\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_